csw.examples.vslice.hcd

Class SingleAxisSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.examples.vslice.hcd.SingleAxisSimulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging, TimeService.TimeServiceScheduler

    public class SingleAxisSimulator
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging, TimeService.TimeServiceScheduler
    This class provides a simulator of a single axis device for the purpose of testing TMT HCDs and Assemblies.

    param: axisConfig an AxisConfig object that contains a description of the axis param: replyTo an actor that will be updated with information while the axis executes
